* after doing this, the web interface will not work.


1) datacenter > firewall > options > double click firewall > check the box

2) pve > firewall >  options > double click firewall > check the box

3) pve > firewall > add:
direction: in
action: DROP

check the "Enable" box


4)refre  web interface



*** to disable this 

in the main proxmox machine shell:


pve-firewall stop
